Description: Builds a single multilevel meta-analysis effects table from
    500+ Cochrane review datasets. Derives TE and seTE for dichotomous and
    continuous outcomes, preserves moderators and provenance (DOI and URL),
    and provides helpers to subset coherent cohorts (e.g., log odds ratios).
    Includes MAFI (Meta-Analysis Fragility Index) for robustness assessment,
    evidence pathway simulation, and Bayesian fragility analysis.
